HOW IT'S MADE
---------------

- Install Go, or download and unarchive.

- To add "rexa" and "regexp2" modules:

    > go get github.com/himclix/rexa@v0.1.0
    > go get github.com/dlclark/regexp2/v2@v2.1.1

    (Adjust the versions)
    
- To build:

    > build.cmd

  (If required, set the path to 'go.exe', or set PATH variable and restart console)

- Commit the changes (including the created "GoWorker.exe").
